data.title: Dentist in Lexington, KY
data.meta_description: Formerly Fayette Family Dentistry and William E. Hampton, D.M.D. We offer you the best quality dental care in Lexington, KY.
data.text:
We strive to provide not only the best treatment but the highest level of comfort when patients step into our office. Wellington Dentistry offers top-of-the-line equipment using new technology in a warm and calming environment. Our skilled doctors work with you to best meet the needs of your unique case, whether you’re seeking cosmetic, restorative, or general dentistry.

From dental crowns to teeth whitening services– to simple routine check-ups– Wellington Dentistry is designed with the patient as the top priority. Drs. Molly Thurmond and William Hampton together have served the Lexington area for decades, and are excited to welcome you to their office.

Call or visit our office to schedule an appointment today!

Our doctors truly believe that each patient is different and will work with you to create a unique treatment plan that specifically fits your needs. With the highest level of training and skill, our doctors are more than capable of providing you with the highest quality dental care in Lexington.

Finding a dentist that you can trust is an important part of maintaining your overall dental health.

We are committed to providing Lexington with the highest quality dentistry in a comfortable and welcoming environment. Experience our calming amenities, friendly dental team, and personalized care that restores your smile and confidence.

Get a natural look you will love with dental crowns and implant crowns. Used to repair and protect teeth that have been worn or damaged, dental crowns and implant crowns add a subtle and afforadable boost to your smile without looking fake or not matching the rest of your smile.

The Wellington Dentistry team is ready to help you determine if dental crowns or implant crowns are right for you!
